00:55:16,510 --> 00:55:18,540
I'm back from school!

699
00:55:18,540 --> 00:55:21,410
Hi. Did you have a good day, Ah Rin?

700
00:55:21,410 --> 00:55:22,680
Yes.

701
00:55:22,680 --> 00:55:24,710
Wash your hands and get ready to go to the academy.

702
00:55:24,710 --> 00:55:28,380
I just got home. Why go to the academy already?

703
00:55:28,380 --> 00:55:29,820
I'm not going.

704
00:55:29,820 --> 00:55:31,980
Did you finish your homework?

705
00:55:34,430 --> 00:55:38,000
How much wealth and prosperity could I possibly get?

706
00:55:40,200 --> 00:55:45,050
Heo Ah Rin, I'll cut your allowance by half if you don't get up immediately.

707
00:55:45,050 --> 00:55:47,140
You can't do that.

708
00:55:48,890 --> 00:55:51,880
Dad, what did you teach her?

709
00:55:51,880 --> 00:55:55,860
I didn't teach her anything. She just picked it up.

710
00:56:07,340 --> 00:56:13,310
♫  If I look at the sky moving further away  ♫

711
00:56:13,310 --> 00:56:19,100
♫  I will leave without any regrets  ♫

712
00:56:19,100 --> 00:56:24,960
♫  Our appearing like we had been together a long time  ♫

713
00:56:24,960 --> 00:56:30,800
♫  will not seem any different  ♫

714
00:56:30,800 --> 00:56:35,910
♫  Dreams will disappear  ♫

715
00:56:35,910 --> 00:56:41,590
♫  The dreams without you will all disappear  ♫

716
00:56:41,590 --> 00:56:43,590
Heo Ah Rin!

717
00:56:45,390 --> 00:56:46,970
Ah Rin—

718
00:56:49,670 --> 00:56:51,460
You took too long. Don't you think?

719
00:56:51,460 --> 00:56:54,430
- You didn't forget anything, right?
 - Of course not.

720
00:56:54,430 --> 00:56:56,160
Let's go.

721
00:56:56,160 --> 00:57:05,760
♫  Even if the paths we have taken are a little different  ♫

722
00:57:05,760 --> 00:57:17,580
♫  I know they are not wrong  ♫

723
00:57:19,720 --> 00:57:21,500
Did you stay up all night?

724
00:57:22,500 --> 00:57:24,310
You came.

725
00:57:24,310 --> 00:57:28,040
Is there a lot to do? Why don't you take it easy?

726
00:57:30,570 --> 00:57:33,060
Instead of saying that to me,

727
00:57:33,060 --> 00:57:37,390
you could say I look cool, I'm doing great, or stuff like that.

728
00:57:37,390 --> 00:57:39,850
I need to hear something like that.

729
00:57:39,850 --> 00:57:43,560
You're doing so great, CEO Yun Te Oh.

730
00:57:44,460 --> 00:57:46,180
Just with words?

731
00:57:47,930 --> 00:57:50,650
You can do stuff like this. You know.

732
00:57:54,680 --> 00:57:56,560
Get some rest.

733
00:57:56,560 --> 00:57:58,460
This is me resting.

734
00:57:58,460 --> 00:58:00,880
I'm recharging right now.

735
00:58:02,970 --> 00:58:07,740
As I mentioned last time, get a wide range of color samples for the bookshelf.

736
00:58:07,740 --> 00:58:09,750
Yes, got it, CEO Seo.

737
00:58:09,750 --> 00:58:11,860
I mean, Team Leader Seo.

738
00:58:11,860 --> 00:58:15,130
I'm still saying that by habit.

739
00:58:15,130 --> 00:58:17,130
I get confused sometimes, too.

740
00:58:17,130 --> 00:58:20,800
I sometimes go to the CEO's office when I get here.

741
00:58:20,800 --> 00:58:24,370
I think CEO Yun would like that.

742
00:58:31,020 --> 00:58:32,980
Have some coffee first.

743
00:58:37,100 --> 00:58:39,440
What's going on here?

744
00:58:39,440 --> 00:58:41,710
Did you talk behind my back?

745
00:58:41,710 --> 00:58:43,650
Thank you so much, Mr. Yun.

746
00:58:43,650 --> 00:58:45,760
Wow, thank you.

747
00:58:45,760 --> 00:58:47,310
Here you go.

748
00:58:51,210 --> 00:58:53,340
That's it for today, right?

749
00:58:53,340 --> 00:58:54,880
Yes, CEO.

750
00:58:54,880 --> 00:59:00,360
I'll rest after confirming the design today, just so you know.

751
00:59:00,360 --> 00:59:03,250
May I work outside the office, then?

752
00:59:03,250 --> 00:59:06,720
Team Leader Seo asked me to join her for market research.

753
00:59:07,310 --> 00:59:09,450
- Market research?
 - Yes.

754
00:59:09,450 --> 00:59:14,180
She wants to browse the new foreign brand shops in Sinsa-dong (a popular Gangnam neighborhood).

755
00:59:14,180 --> 00:59:15,840
Go ahead.

756
00:59:18,290 --> 00:59:20,040
CEO,

757
00:59:20,040 --> 00:59:26,870
I'm suddenly thinking it might be better for an expert to join her instead.

758
00:59:29,660 --> 00:59:35,960
Yes, I guess an expert should go since it's so important.

759
00:59:40,110 --> 00:59:41,910
Thank you, Seong Hui.

760
00:59:54,640 --> 00:59:56,110
CEO.

761
00:59:59,530 --> 01:00:02,380
We've walked a lot. Aren't you tired?

762
01:00:02,380 --> 01:00:06,990
No, I'm okay. I got to see new furniture, too.

763
01:00:10,940 --> 01:00:13,590
Building a house somewhere like this,

764
01:00:13,590 --> 01:00:17,450
raising children, making furniture,

765
01:00:19,310 --> 01:00:22,420
and living with someone you love.

766
01:00:22,420 --> 01:00:24,520
What do you think of that?

767
01:00:28,410 --> 01:00:30,750
Why do you look at me like that?

768
01:00:30,750 --> 01:00:32,220
Te Oh,

769
01:00:33,120 --> 01:00:34,700
thank you.

770
01:00:35,530 --> 01:00:38,030
Why all of a sudden?

771
01:00:38,030 --> 01:00:40,850
At some point,

772
01:00:41,990 --> 01:00:46,590
I started taking having you with me for granted.

773
01:00:46,590 --> 01:00:50,250
I think I've forgotten how precious that is.

774
01:00:52,820 --> 01:00:55,740
I'm sorry I realized that too late.

775
01:01:02,100 --> 01:01:07,060
Why does your thanks sound like a goodbye to me?

776
01:01:07,060 --> 01:01:09,010
Because we can't keep going like this.

777
01:01:09,010 --> 01:01:11,090
Why can't we?

778
01:01:11,090 --> 01:01:16,050
I'll surely continue to be by your side going forward.

779
01:01:16,050 --> 01:01:18,670
Because I have an illness.

780
01:01:18,670 --> 01:01:20,110
What's wrong with that?

781
01:01:20,110 --> 01:01:21,620
It's an important matter.

782
01:01:21,620 --> 01:01:24,000
Yes, it's important.

783
01:01:24,000 --> 01:01:27,020
But that's not everything that defines you.

784
01:01:27,740 --> 01:01:32,560
You have a lot more valuable things than that illness.

785
01:01:32,560 --> 01:01:34,880
You're pretty,

786
01:01:36,970 --> 01:01:39,260
cute,

787
01:01:39,930 --> 01:01:42,400
and you're adorable, too.

788
01:01:43,300 --> 01:01:47,040
The fact that you're ill is just a tiny...

789
01:01:47,040 --> 01:01:51,300
nothing but a tiny little part of you.

790
01:01:51,300 --> 01:01:54,160
That's not entirely Seo Jae Won.

791
01:01:55,640 --> 01:01:58,900
So, don't try to reject me using that.

792
01:02:02,240 --> 01:02:04,370
I won't rush things.

793
01:02:04,370 --> 01:02:06,120
So...

794
01:02:07,810 --> 01:02:10,430
just don't push me away.

795
01:02:19,680 --> 01:02:22,970
It might take a long time.

796
01:02:22,970 --> 01:02:24,960
Would that be okay?

797
01:02:26,470 --> 01:02:28,880
Do you mean...

798
01:02:32,620 --> 01:02:35,820
Of course! Of course, I can wait.

799
01:02:35,820 --> 01:02:38,130
You scared me.

800
01:02:38,130 --> 01:02:40,140
How long do I have to wait?

801
01:02:40,140 --> 01:02:43,500
It's not that I'm impatient.

802
01:02:43,500 --> 01:02:46,570
It'd be nice to know a rough date. Until when?

803
01:02:46,570 --> 01:02:49,840
I need to go. Ah Rin will be back soon.

804
01:02:49,840 --> 01:02:52,140
So, until when should I wait?

805
01:02:52,140 --> 01:02:54,500
Not until Ah Rin gets married or anything like that, right?

806
01:02:54,500 --> 01:02:56,260
I need to hurry. I need to go.

807
01:02:56,260 --> 01:02:58,330
Please tell me, CEO. Please!

808
01:02:58,330 --> 01:03:03,300
You achieved a lot more things than I expected.

809
01:03:04,880 --> 01:03:09,510
I'll accept myself for who I am now.

810
01:03:09,510 --> 01:03:16,470
And the three people whom I thought turned their backs on me,

811
01:03:16,470 --> 01:03:20,090
I'll remember the fact

812
01:03:20,090 --> 01:03:25,820
that they were the most precious people who stood by me.

813
01:03:31,470 --> 01:03:36,020
You need to continue your treatment going forward.

814
01:03:36,020 --> 01:03:37,850
Yes, Doctor.

815
01:03:40,960 --> 01:03:42,950
Thank you.

816
01:03:44,050 --> 01:03:50,070
I've been wanting to tell you that in person at least once.

817
